Subject: Re: [VB] Big tires on a pickup


I'm running 215/15 rears and 195/14 fronts on both my busses.  Does have a
tilt, which I think changes the camber enough to notice it in the
steering.  My 58 has always steered very nice until I did this.  Although
it's not bad it is noticeable that it's a little touchier.
John K.



